    <div class="card">
        <h2>How to Delete Your Data</h2>

        <div class="highlight info">
            <strong>Good news:</strong> All your dream data is stored locally on your device, not on external servers. You have complete control over your data.
        </div>

        <p>To delete all your data from NightMind, follow these steps:</p>

        <ol>
            <li>Open the <strong>NightMind</strong> app on your device</li>
            <li>Tap the <strong>Settings</strong> icon (gear icon)</li>
            <li>Scroll down to find <strong>"Delete All Data"</strong></li>
            <li>Tap <strong>"Delete All Data"</strong></li>
            <li>Confirm the deletion when prompted</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="highlight warning">
            <strong>Warning:</strong> This action is permanent and cannot be undone. All your dream entries, settings, and generated videos will be permanently deleted from your device.
        </div>

        <h2>What Gets Deleted</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>All dream journal entries</li>
            <li>All generated videos and thumbnails</li>
            <li>All AI dream analyses</li>
            <li>App settings and preferences</li>
            <li>Local encryption keys</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data on External Services</h2>
        <p>NightMind uses minimal external services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Device ID:</strong> An anonymous identifier used for rate limiting. This is not linked to any personal information and cannot be used to identify you.</li>
            <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> If you made purchases, RevenueCat maintains purchase records as required by Apple/Google. Contact RevenueCat directly for purchase-related data requests.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Alternative: Uninstall the App</h2>
        <p>Uninstalling NightMind from your device will also remove all locally stored data, including your dream entries and generated content.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about data deletion or need assistance, contact:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@nightmind.ai</p>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>

